{"word":"ῥῆγος","slug":"ῥῆγος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92324\" key=\"r(h=gos\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥῆγος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, <sense id=\"n92324.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">rug, blanket</tr_>, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> mostly in pl. (sg. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:661\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.661</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:13:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.73</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:118\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">118</biblScope> </bibl>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥ. καλά, πορφύρεα</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:644\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.644</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:297\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.297</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σιγαλόεντα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.38</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:189\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.189</biblScope></bibl>, etc.: used as covering of a bed, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:661\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.661</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:24:644\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.644</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:349\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.349</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; or of a seat, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:10:352\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.352</biblScope> </bibl>; prob. a garment, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:6:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.38</biblScope> </bibl>: since, in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:13:73\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.73</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:118\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">118</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> distinguishes <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥῆγος</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λίνον</foreign>, it is prob. that the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥῆγος</foreign> was of wool. (from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ῥῆξαι,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">